   "text": "(1) If the minister requires land for habitat for a species of wildlife designated as an endangered species or threatened species, the minister may, by regulation, designate land in a wildlife management area as a critical wildlife area.\n(2) The minister may, by regulation, designate land in a wildlife management area as a wildlife sanctuary."
