orm analyses and tests;\n(c) take photographs of\n(i) a vehicle,\n(ii) an aircraft designed to land on water,\n(iii) a boat,\n(iv) any water-related equipment, or\n(v) water, aquatic invasive species or suspected aquatic invasive species that are in or on a vehicle, aircraft, boat or equipment referred to in subparagraphs (i) to (iv);\n(d) make copies of relevant records."
